<h3>
CfP: Tracing the Heroic through Gender. 1650 – 1750 – 1850
</h3>
</div>
<div class='well'>
<p class=''>
<b>
Ort:
</b>
Freiburg
</p>
<p class=''>
<b>
Frist:
</b>
2014-03-28
</p>
<p class=''>
<b>
